    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルさん\nまたパフォーマンスが上がったみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ TRINITYAiLE.\nThey’ve outdone themselves yet again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6114961951971054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "今のところ、凄い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That part just now was amazing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.165264280025776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 9.931930946692441
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 9.931930946692441
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "はーい、曲はTRINITYAiLEで\n『Aile to Yell』でしたー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank ya'll kindly! We're TRINITYAiLE\nAnd that there was our tune‚ \"Aile to Yell\"!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.098597613359107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 16.265264280025775
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "では、続いてはこちら\n『便りがないのは、いいおたより。』のコーナー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And next up‚\nwe have our “No Problems is a Good Problem” corner.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.231930946692447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 20.86526428002578
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "私達がみんなの送ってくれた悩みを解決して\n悩みのお便りがなくなるまで頑張るというコーナーです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right here‚ we aim to fix all them troubles y'all send our way\ntil everyone of ya stops havin' troubles to fuss about!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.43193094669245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 28.365264280025784
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "はいはーい、では一枚目のお便りは――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okaaay! Now‚ for our first problem today‚ we have…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.365264280025784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 32.10134135026202
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（TRINITYAiLEはバンプロ所属のグループだ）\n（さくら達と同年代ながらその人気はトップクラス）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（TRINITYAiLE is a Van Productions idol group.）\n（Even though they’re no older than Sakura’s group‚ they’re top-class.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.40134135026199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 39.9346746835953
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いずれ、自分達も同じことをするかもしれない\nそのつもりでね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Watch.\nThat might be you someday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.23467468359532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 45.72042729903069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! Right…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.72042729903069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ\nさくらちゃんの放送は面白そうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe.\nI’m sure you’d be great on TV‚ Sakura-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらが呼びに行くと琴乃は素直に戻ってきた）\n（黙ってはいたが、自分が悪かったと思っているようだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sakura went to Kotono‚ and she rejoined the group.）\n（She didn't say anything but looks apologetic.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.133115069940686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃はどう思う？\nこんな放送があったら、何を喋る？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think‚ Kotono?\nWhat would you talk about if you're on the show?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.33723464689356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？\n………………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?\n…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.44238963804345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "放送事故かも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’d probably choke.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.74238963804343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "もしラジオだったら喋ってないと\n放送してないのと同じだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have to keep talking constantly‚\notherwise‚ it’s like you’re not even on air.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.72572287600933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、違うの\n今のは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ no\nI didn’t say anything because…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.32572287600934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "なんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.62572287600933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……なんでもない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Never mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.45905620934268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、後で練習しようよ\n私もお喋り苦手だし、すぐ黙って考えちゃう方だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s practice later‚ Kotono-chan.\nI'm bad at public speaking‚ too. I get in my head too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.72572287600936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……うん……ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay… Thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.22752732820275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（素直に礼を言うところを見ると）\n（渚への信頼度は高いようだ）\n（そう考えると）\n（やはり渚を入れたのは間違いないだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It’s clear from how Kotono opens up to Nagisa）\n（that she really trusts her.）\n（In this sense‚）\n（it was the right move to bring Nagisa into the group.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（だが練習を見ていて、それぞれ個性のある）\n（この五人が、すぐにまとまっていくようには見えない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Yet‚ as I watch them practice‚ it’s hard to picture）\n（these five very different girls coming together as a team.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.83183544637728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（どんなグループを目指すのか）\n（そこに辿り着くにはまだ時間が必要な気がするな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It looks like they’re going to need some time to figure out）\n（what kind of group they’ll aim to be and how they’ll get there.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.56439142696132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage3",
      "startTime": 116.59772476029471
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshidorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 117.09772476029472
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "では、決めたいと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ I’d like to decide something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.89772476029476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "決めるって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Decide what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.11738456559262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "これからの当番表です、不公平にならないように\nちゃんとしないと――という訳で作ってきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our household duties. I wanted to keep it as fair as possible‚\nso I drew up this schedule.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.95071789892592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
